# YP Monorepo - 1Password Environment Variables
# =============================================
# Usage: op run --env-file=.env.1password -- <command>
# Example: op run --env-file=.env.1password -- pnpm dev
#
# SETUP:
# 1. Create a 1Password item called "YP Monorepo" in your Private vault
# 2. Add each field name below (e.g., BETTER_AUTH_SECRET)
# 3. Fill in your actual values in 1Password
# 4. Run commands with `op run --env-file=.env.1password -- <command>`
#
# Adjust "Private" to your vault name if different.
# =============================================

